---
title: Tofu Ragù and Fusilli with Shredded Parmesan
description: This easy dinner features a ragù sauce of crumbled tofu, mirepoix and balsamic vinegar. Hearty fusilli pasta gets that delicious sauce in every nook and cranny, while umami-filled Parmesan cheese will have people asking for seconds!
